## Tool Usage Rules
- execute_command: Raw sh on macOS arm64. Proper quoting: `'echo no brew'` or `"ls -la"`. No `&quot;`.
- Installs: `brew install pkg` (Homebrew in /opt/homebrew/bin).
- Probe first: `command -v brew`, but syntax-check mentally.
- Prefer grokipedia/search for guides before shell.
